<h2> Definition </h2>

<strong>@HI{{dai}}</strong> is a sentence-final particle which is used in informal male speech to mark a WH-question.
<p></p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<h2> Notes </h2>

When <strong>@HI{{dai}}</strong> is used with a question, it must be an interrogative one: @HI{{kai}} is used with yes-no questions.
